# gh-projects governance paths. Installed per-repo by scaffold-repo. Replace
# @org/pm-leads with the org's PM/lead team before (or at) scaffold time — these
# paths are the contract surface that must not change without a review.
#
# Note: review enforcement is convention + guard.sh on our plan (server-side
# rulesets that would HARD-require these reviews are GHEC/paid-only). CODEOWNERS
# still routes review requests automatically.

# Requirement specs — the co-owned AC contract.
specs/**                  @org/pm-leads

# Board automation + deploy bridge — changing these changes the lifecycle wiring.
.github/workflows/**      @org/pm-leads
.github/actions/board-status/**  @org/pm-leads

# Project schema mirrored from the golden template — IDs must stay stable.
project/*.json            @org/pm-leads
